      "amount": "4 cups"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Mix all ingredients for the crumble base in a bowl.",
    "Add the bouquet garni to the almond milk or coconut milk and simmer gently until fragrant, about 10 minutes. Strain into the crumble base.",
    "Blend the mixture until smooth, then stir in oat flour while hot.",
    "Pour the crumbly mixture into a baking dish and chill for at least 2 hours before serving.",
    "Serve chilled with fruit or on its own."
